text: Kot Guraya is a town in the Punjab province of Pakistan. It is located in Lahore District at 31°15'0N 73°8'0E, at an altitude of 168 metres (554 feet) and lies near to the city of Lahore.Location of Gobindsar - Falling Rain Genomics Neighbouring settlements include Singh Khalsa and Gobindsar. ==References== Category:Populated places in Lahore District
title: Kot Guraya
